nl_command: observation of Indigo Grill releases The Market By Buon Appetito from holding true
ltl: U the_market_by_buon_appetito indigo_grill

nl_command: observation of Lofty Coffee & co. releases Salt & Straw from holding true
ltl: U salt_&_straw lofty_coffee_&_co.
result: & G ! lofty_coffee_&_co. )lm G salt_&_straw lm( lofty_coffee_&_co.

nl_command: stay at Wells Fargo till Burger Lounge occurs
ltl: U wells_fargo burger_lounge

nl_command: stay at Salt & Straw till Mexican Consulate occurs
ltl: U salt_&_straw mexican_consulate

nl_command: till Harbor Breakfast occurs do not exit La Vita Little Italy
ltl: U la_vita_little_italy harbor_breakfast

nl_command: till Little Italy occurs do not exit ITH Eco Farm House San Diego
ltl: U ith_eco_farm_house_san_diego little_italy
result: G ! queenstown )lm )lm salt_&_straw lm( salt_&_straw lm( salt_&_straw lm(

nl_command: remain at Farmers Market (Wed and Sat) as long as La Vita Little Italy is not seen
ltl: U farmers_market_(wed_and_sat) la_vita_little_italy

nl_command: remain at Queenstown as long as Mexican Consulate is not seen
ltl: U queenstown mexican_consulate

nl_command: wait at Salt & Straw till you see Firehouse Museum
ltl: U salt_&_straw firehouse_museum

nl_command: wait at The Market By Buon Appetito till you see Davanti Enoteca
ltl: U the_market_by_buon_appetito davanti_enoteca

nl_command: hold position at ITH Eco Farm House San Diego for as long as Little Italy does not occur
ltl: U ith_eco_farm_house_san_diego little_italy

nl_command: hold position at Piazza della Famiglia for as long as Lofty Coffee & co. does not occur
ltl: U piazza_della_famiglia lofty_coffee_&_co.

nl_command: as long as you do not see Piazza della Famiglia happen do not leave Wells Fargo
ltl: U wells_fargo piazza_della_famiglia

nl_command: as long as you do not see Lofty Coffee & co. happen do not leave Indigo Grill
ltl: U indigo_grill lofty_coffee_&_co.
